articles.author: GERALD IMRAY Associated Press
articles.title: Snake on a plane! South African pilot finds cobra under seat - ABC News
articles.description: A pilot in South Africa made a hasty emergency landing after discovering a highly venomous cobra hiding under his seat
articles.content:
CAPE TOWN, South Africa -- A pilot in South Africa made a hasty emergency landing after discovering a highly venomous cobra hiding under his seat.
